<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Page Not Found | Gallformers</title>
    <meta name="description" content="The requested page was not found on Gallformers." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Page Not Found | Gallformers" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="The requested page was not found on Gallformers." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://gallformers.org/images/cynipid_R.svg" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Gallformers" />
    <link phx-track-static rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/app.css"} />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'League Spartan', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
      }
      .container {
        min-height: 60vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      .card {
        text-align: center;
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        max-width: 32rem;
      }
      .status-code {
        font-size: 3.75rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #661419;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .description {
        color: #4b5563;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .image {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .buttons {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      @media (min-width: 640px) {
        .buttons {
          flex-direction: row;
        }
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.15s ease;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background-color: #661419;
        color: white;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #bc6428;
      }
      .btn-secondary {
        border: 1px solid #661419;
        color: #661419;
        background: transparent;
      }
      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="status-code">404</div>
        <h1 class="title">This Page Was Not Found</h1>
        <p class="description">
          Notably this is also not a gall, though it sure does look like one.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/58767231"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/scale.jpg"
            alt="A scale insect not a gall"
            class="image"
            onerror="this.classList.add('hidden')"
          />
        </a>
        <div class="buttons">
          <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-primary">Go Back</a>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Go Home</a>
          <a href="/id" class="btn btn-secondary">Try our ID tool</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
